[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 19    [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;192;197;206mA second wrinkle that makes wellness recommendation distinct from anything in Recipes 4.1, 4.2, or 4.3: the unit of "success" is months long. A patient confirming an appointment (4.1) is a same-day signal. A patient clicking on an education article (4.2) is a same-day signal. A patient choosing a provider (4.3) is a same-week signal. A patient enrolling in a 12-week DPP, attending sessions, losing weight, and (the actual outcome you cared about) not progressing to type 2 diabetes within three years, is a multi-year signal. The recommender has to make decisions every day with feedback loops measured in months and quarters. That changes the architecture, the evaluation strategy, and the kinds of mistakes you can afford to make.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     19[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mA second wrinkle that makes wellness recommendation distinct from anything in Recipes 4.1, 4.2, or 4.3: the unit of "success" is months long. A patient confirming an appointment (4.1) is a same-day signal. A patient clicking on an education article (4.2) is a same-day signal. A patient choosing a provider (4.3) is a same-week signal. A patient enrolling in a 12-month DPP, attending sessions, losing weight, and (the actual outcome you cared about) not progressing to type 2 diabetes within three years, is a multi-year signal. The recommender has to make decisions every day with feedback loops measured in months and quarters. That changes the architecture, the evaluation strategy, and the kinds of mistakes you can afford to make.[K
